To update git repository
sh MAJ.sh

------------------------

To make the library accessible, copy the lines
of interest to bashrc :

export CPLUS_INCLUDE_PATH=/path/to/Nuball2/lib:$CPLUS_INCLUDE_PATH
export CPLUS_INCLUDE_PATH=/path/to/Nuball2/lib/MTObjects:$CPLUS_INCLUDE_PATH
export CPLUS_INCLUDE_PATH=/path/to/Nuball2/lib/Classes:$CPLUS_INCLUDE_PATH
export CPLUS_INCLUDE_PATH=/path/to/Nuball2/lib/Analyse:$CPLUS_INCLUDE_PATH

or 

source /path/to/Nuball2/lib/source.sh